articles.title: Where to See the Artemis I Mission Liftoff to the Moon - NASA
articles.description: This infographic labeled “Artemis I: Visibility Range” depicts the areas that could potentially spot Artemis I after liftoff. The Space Launch System rocket and Orion spacecraft could be seen along the Space Coast for up to 70 seconds after liftoff.
